	<article class='post' id="post-1680453" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article">

		<h1 id="headline" itemprop="url headline name">For Ebola Patients in Sierra Leone, Survival Takes More Than Medicine</h1>
<link itemprop="url" href="http://www.wired.com/2014/12/ebola-patients-sierra-leone-survival-takes-medecine/" />
<link itemprop="image" href="http://www.wired.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/ebola-tent.jpg" />

<ul class="entry-header">
	
	<li class="author">By&nbsp;<a rel="author" href="http://www.wired.com/author/erikacheck/">Erika Check Hayden</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>

	<li class="entryDate"><time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2014-12-16T06:45:28-05:00">12.16.14</time>&nbsp;&nbsp;&#124;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
	<li class="entryTime">6:45 am&nbsp;&nbsp;&#124;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>

