            <li class="twitter-small">
            <a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/share?text=For+Ebola+Patients+in+Sierra+Leone%2C+Survival+Takes+More+Than+Medicine+%7C+WIRED&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2F2014%2F12%2Febola-patients-sierra-leone-survival-takes-medecine%2F" class="twitter-share-button" data-lang="en">Tweet</a>
